{"type":"message","id":"1a2c18d7","parentId":"c2047c27","timestamp":"2026-04-03T07:06:56.134Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The cron jobs are all failing with: `\"lastError\": \"Delivering to Feishu requires target <chatId|user:openId|chat:chatId>\"`\n\nThis is a delivery configuration issue. The cron job is trying to deliver to Feishu but the `target` field is set to `user:ou_e48f6c4c0395f45b74b51525f348678b` which should be the correct format. \n\nWait, let me re-read the error: `\"lastError\": \"Delivering to Feishu requires target <chatId|user:openId|chat:chatId>\"` - this seems like the target IS specified correctly... but the delivery is still failing. \n \nThe message is being delivered to an agent session rather than directly to the channel, which is causing the issue. The payload uses `kind: \"agentTurn\"` which means it goes to an isolated session first, and then that session tries to send the message—but the direct delivery mode doesn't seem to be properly routing back to Feishu.\n\nLooking at the actual error and the user's ID `ou_e48f6c4c0395f45b74b51525f348678b`, the Feishu plugin might not recognize the `user:` prefix format when it's actually trying to deliver. The session might have crashed or the Feishu message sending itself failed, even though the target appears correctly formatted. I'm checking the cron job configuration and I see the real issue now—the `delivery.target` format looks correct with `user:ou_e48f6c4c0395f45b74b51525f348678b`, but the jobs are failing because the agent session can't actually send messages to Feishu, not because of a malformed target address.\n\nSince both jobs have `consecutiveErrors: 4` and the same delivery error, I should restart the Gateway to clear out any stuck sessions or state, then diagnose what's preventing Feishu delivery from working in the isolated session context."},{"type":"text","text":"找到问题了！Cron 任务都报错：\n\n```\nlastError: \"Delivering to Feishu requires target <chatId|user:openId|chat:chatId>\"\n```\n\n4次连续失败，疑似 Gateway 信使故障。我来重启一下：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_k4m8pn5mn81y_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw gateway restart","yieldMs":8000,"timeout":15}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775199994493}}
