{"type":"message","id":"a04f9637","parentId":"267a4a17","timestamp":"2026-04-03T07:12:21.605Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The script ran successfully but got 0 feeds. This means the MCP is connected but returned empty feeds. The cookie might be invalid or expired. Let me check the push results file to understand more.\n\nLet me try the search_feeds tool directly via the MCP to see if it works."},{"type":"text","text":"连上了！但 Feeds 返回 0 条——Cookie 可能过期了。先验证下 MCP 是否正常工作：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gv17heqjtftc_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python - << 'PY'\nimport requests, json\n\ns = requests.Session()\nhdrs = {'Accept': 'application/json, text/event-stream'}\nr1 = s.post('http://localhost:18060/mcp', json={\n    'jsonrpc':'2.0','id':1,'method':'initialize',\n    'params':{'protocolVersion':'2024-11-05','capabilities':{},'clientInfo':{'name':'openclaw','version':'1.0'}}\n}, headers=hdrs, timeout=10)\nhdrs['Mcp-Session-Id'] = r1.headers.get('Mcp-Session-Id', '')\ns.post('http://localhost:18060/mcp', json={'jsonrpc':'2.0','method':'notifications/initialized'}, headers=hdrs)\n\n# check login status\nresp = s.post('http://localhost:18060/mcp', json={\n    'jsonrpc':'2.0','id':2,'method':'tools/call',\n    'params':{'name':'check_login_status','arguments':{}}\n}, headers=hdrs, timeout=15)\nprint(resp.json())\nPY","yieldMs":30000,"timeout":40}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775200331183}}
{"type":"message","id":"5a8331a6","parentId":"a04f9637","timestamp":"2026-04-03T07:12:21.871Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_gv17heqjtftc_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"����λ�� ��:1 �ַ�: 11\r\n+ python - << 'PY'\r\n+           ~\r\n�ض������������ȱ���ļ��淶��\r\n����λ�� ��:1 �ַ�: 10\r\n+ python - << 'PY'\r\n+          ~\r\n��<���������Ϊ����ʹ�ö������ġ�\r\n����λ�� ��:1 �ַ�: 11\r\n+ python - << 'PY'\r\n+           ~\r\n��<���������Ϊ����ʹ�ö������ġ�\r\n����λ�� ��:4 �ַ�: 22\r\n+ s = requests.Session()\r\n+                      ~\r\n��(������ӦΪ����ʽ��\r\n����λ�� ��:5 �ַ�: 17\r\n+ hdrs = {'Accept': 'application/json, text/event-stream'}\r\n+                 ~\r\n����ʽ������а�������ı�ǡ�:����\r\n����λ�� ��:6 �ַ�: 42\r\n+ r1 = s.post('http://localhost:18060/mcp', json={\r\n+                                          ~\r\n��,������ȱ�ٱ���ʽ��\r\n����λ�� ��:6 �ַ�: 43\r\n+ r1 = s.post('http://localhost:18060/mcp', json={\r\n+                                           ~~~~~\r\n����ʽ������а�������ı�ǡ�json=����\r\n����λ�� ��:6 �ַ�: 42\r\n+ r1 = s.post('http://localhost:18060/mcp', json={\r\n+                                          ~\r\n����ʽ��ȱ���ҡ�)����\r\n����λ�� ��:7 �ַ�: 14\r\n+     'jsonrpc':'2.0','id':1,'method':'initialize',\r\n+              ~~~~~~\r\n����ʽ������а�������ı�ǡ�:'2.0'����\r\n����λ�� ��:7 �ַ�: 20\r\n+     'jsonrpc':'2.0','id':1,'method':'initialize',\r\n+                    ~\r\n�����б���ȱ�ٲ�����\r\n��δ�������з����������������Ĵ������ԡ�\r\n    + CategoryInfo          : ParserError: (:) [], ParentContainsErrorRecordException\r\n    + FullyQualifiedErrorId : MissingFileSpecification\n\n(Command exited with code 1)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":1,"durationMs":256,"aggregated":"����λ�� ��:1 �ַ�: 11\r\n+ python - << 'PY'\r\n+           ~\r\n�ض������������ȱ���ļ��淶��\r\n����λ�� ��:1 �ַ�: 10\r\n+ python - << 'PY'\r\n+          ~\r\n��<���������Ϊ����ʹ�ö������ġ�\r\n����λ�� ��:1 �ַ�: 11\r\n+ python - << 'PY'\r\